fter all,nutrition fuels athletic performance.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"After all,nutrition fuels\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"athletic performance\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, some athletes come from places where malnutrition is a constant concern.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some athletes\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"malnutrition\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"a constant concern\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In many parts of the world, hunger is deeply linked to conflict, which has beenon the rise.\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many parts\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"hunger\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than117 million peoplewere forcibly displaced last year.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than117 million peoplewere\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can create a vicious cycle, as many displaced people face hunger and uncertainty.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a vicious cycle\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"many displaced people\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"hunger\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"uncertainty\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, their stories do not have to end there.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their stories\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1464}]}, {\"se